# Root-context .dockerignore for the backend-ts image build (#109 PR1).
#
# Only ./backend-ts and ./external/mieweb-cloud are COPYed into that image; this trims the build
# context the daemon receives from the repo root. The Java backend (./backend) and the frontend
# (./frontend) images build from their OWN subdirectory contexts, so this file does not affect them.
.git
**/node_modules
**/.data
backend
frontend
e2e
docs
*.pdf
*.md
